\id ROM Matupi Chin Standard Bible
\h ROM
\toc1 ROM
\toc2 Rom
\toc3 Rom
\mt1 ROM
\mt2 (Paul’s Letter to the Romans)
\imt1 ROM CAPAT KAWNG
\ip Hekah cabu dongah he Paul loh Rom kho kah Khrihca hlangboel taengah amah kawng neh olthangthen kawng a thui pah. Amah he Rom khopuei ah om pawt dae Khrihca rhoek loh anih te bahoeng a lamtawn uh. (15.22—-16.21). Amah he caeltueih la om tih olthangthen aka phong la a tuek (1.1). Pathen kah khangnah he hlang tom boeih Judah, Gentles boeih ham ni. (1.16).
\ip Paul loh mamih boeih he tah Pathen thangpomnah neh aka tingtawk pawh hlangtholh rhoek ni a ti (3.23). Te koinih Pathen kah kolonah la metlam n'om thai eh? Hekah a kawng ni Paul loh amah kah capat dongah a thui. Ol a tongnah dongah Pathen kongaih bang hlang boeih a hing thai moenih a ti. Judah rhoek loh Moses kah olkhueng te a poe uh tih Gentiles rhoek loh Pathen kopoek te a hnawt uh. Pathen loh amih ham a hnuk a hmai la ol a thui a ti. (1.18—-3.20).
\ip Rom capat he AD 56-57 tluk, Paul Korin kho ah a om vaengah a tael.
\iot Sawt Yoeinah
\io1 Paul neh Pathen kah olthangthen \ior (1. 1-17)\ior*
\io1 Hlang tom he boeih tholh \ior (1. 18—3. 20)\ior*
\io1 Pathen loh pilnam a doenah a longim \ior (3. 21—4. 25)\ior*
\io1 Pathen kah pilnam ham hingnah thai \ior (5. 1—8. 39)\ior*
\io1 Israel ca rhoek kah moeiboe \ior (9. 1—11. 36)\ior*
\io1 Lungnah neh hingnah thai \ior (12. 1—15. 13)\ior*
\io1 Paul kah toidal nah \ior (15. 14—16. 27)\ior*
\c 1
\s1 Rom ham Olthangthen
\p 
